37:50.101 --> 37:51.769
Drink it, Wally...

37:51.895 --> 37:54.313
and then I'll be glad to hear
anything you have to say.

37:56.024 --> 37:58.359
You'll find out that
no one named Wooley...

37:58.526 --> 38:00.653
is able to stay
away from me.

38:01.863 --> 38:05.282
Oh, i'm awfully sorry.
This is terrible.

38:05.408 --> 38:08.035
Jennifer! Jennifer!
Can you hear me?

38:08.161 --> 38:10.287
Dudley! Come here!

38:10.413 --> 38:13.874
Oh, you —
Here, here. Drink this.

38:15.210 --> 38:16.543
There.

38:16.711 --> 38:18.879
There, that's better.

38:19.047 --> 38:21.632
Now, how do you feel?

38:21.758 --> 38:24.301
I — I feel strange.

38:24.427 --> 38:26.095
- Hmm?
- What happened?

38:26.221 --> 38:29.014
