- What's that smoke?

39:59.147 --> 40:01.315
- What happened to him?
- Who?

40:01.441 --> 40:04.193
The fellow we pulled
out of the fire. He's gone!

40:05.236 --> 40:07.279
How do you like my body, Jennifer?

40:07.405 --> 40:11.075
Not too old, not too young.
I'm sorry I've forgotten
the formula for clothing.

40:11.201 --> 40:13.660
I had to borrow this sheet
from the ambulance.

40:13.787 --> 40:17.206
By the by, has the potion
been administered?

40:17.332 --> 40:18.791
Yes.

40:18.917 --> 40:22.252
Father, something
went wrong with our plan.

40:22.378 --> 40:24.963
What?
But that love philter never fails.

40:25.090 --> 40:27.007
It didn't.

40:27.175 --> 40:29.301
But... I drank it.

40:29.427 --> 40:32.971
Nicodemus!
Then you love him!

40:33.098 --> 40:34.848
Yes, Father.

40:34.974 --> 40:37.184
