to marry someone else...

40:37.310 --> 40:39.978
because of my ancient curse
on the Wooleys.

40:40.105 --> 40:42.481
Do you think
if I explained it all to him —

40:42.607 --> 40:46.693
By all means do.
Telling a mortal you're a witch
will only mean the end of you.

40:46.861 --> 40:49.738
Then what shall I do?
He must not marry her.

40:49.864 --> 40:52.199
You won't let him, will you?

40:52.367 --> 40:55.035
- Let me think.
- You could make him love me.

40:55.161 --> 40:57.830
You can do
anything you want.

40:57.956 --> 40:59.373
Yes.

40:59.499 --> 41:02.751
This problem should be
fairly simple.

41:02.877 --> 41:06.630
- Just leave it all to me.
- Oh, thank you, Father!

41:06.756 --> 41:08.882
- Will you leave it to me?
- i promise.

41:09.008 --> 41:10.467
Splendid.

41:11.970 --> 41:15.222
[ Chuckles ] I'm still
a little bit warm from the fire.

41:15.390 --> 41:19.059
Jennifer, fetch me a pair
of Master Wooley's breeches.

41:19.185 --> 41:21.061
