"I'm a seeing-eye dog" now.

42:20.455 --> 42:22.998
- Can't you smile?
- You know I wanted
a church wedding.

42:23.124 --> 42:24.958
You've had everything else
your own way.

42:25.084 --> 42:28.003
I should never have given in
to Wallace. It's the last time.

42:29.422 --> 42:31.715
She's not here.
Stop worrying.

42:31.841 --> 42:33.842
