44:05.184 --> 44:07.519
- Would you excuse us?
- Maybe you'd better.

44:07.645 --> 44:09.646
Hurry up.
I'll stand guard.

44:09.772 --> 44:12.524
Let me fix your pretty tie.
You see, Father?

44:12.650 --> 44:14.901
He's just like a Greek god.

44:15.028 --> 44:18.530
My little one tells me
she was your overnight guest.

44:18.656 --> 44:21.366
- Not at my invitation.
- Oh, no, Father.

44:21.492 --> 44:23.410
The poor sweet
didn't want me to stay.

44:23.578 --> 44:26.496
Were I an ordinary man,
Master Wooley...

44:26.622 --> 44:29.291
a horsewhipping
would no doubt be in order.

44:29.417 --> 44:32.961
