44:51.564 --> 44:53.315
Here is a bruised flower.

44:53.441 --> 44:56.109
I am her father.

44:56.235 --> 44:58.278
That is your revolver.

44:58.404 --> 45:02.157
You are going to shoot me.

45:02.283 --> 45:06.161
