45:08.122 --> 45:11.750
Now, now.
Father knows best.

45:11.876 --> 45:14.044
Warm, Master Wooley?

45:14.170 --> 45:16.963
You don't know
what warmth is.

45:17.090 --> 45:21.301
I am told one of your forebears
made a hobby of bonfires.

45:21.427 --> 45:23.887
What a pity
he cannot be here...

45:24.013 --> 45:25.931
to see
his descendant burn.

45:26.057 --> 45:28.642
Yes, Master Wooley.

45:30.144 --> 45:32.938
Burn.
In the modern way.

45:33.064 --> 45:35.148
Strapped in a chair...

45:35.274 --> 45:37.359
heated by electricity.

45:41.406 --> 45:43.407
I anticipated that.

45:43.533 --> 45:45.909
Pistol, pistol, let there be...

45:46.035 --> 45:48.745
murder in the first degree.

45:51.290 --> 45:54.626
Thank you so much.

45:54.752 --> 45:57.796
Amusing invention,
the electric chair.

45:57.922 --> 46:01.842
[ Chuckles ]
