46:02.009 --> 46:04.219
next?

46:08.182 --> 46:11.476
- What's happened?
- Uh —

46:11.602 --> 46:14.521
- It was an accident!
- 'Twas no accident.

46:14.689 --> 46:16.606
He killed me in cold blood.

46:16.732 --> 46:19.359
Kindly notify the authorities.

46:21.612 --> 46:23.864
Oh, he's frightened you.

46:24.031 --> 46:25.949
He told me he'd help me.

46:29.871 --> 46:32.038
- [ Wallace ] How is he?
- He's dead.

46:32.165 --> 46:35.417
Oh, it doesn't matter.

46:35.543 --> 46:38.086
"Doesn't matter"?
Her own father!

46:38.212 --> 46:40.005
Oh, but that's not
my father.

46:40.131 --> 46:42.591
That's just a body
he picked up.

46:43.676 --> 46:46.094
I didn't do it, Dudley!
You'll be my witness!

46:46.220 --> 46:48.346
All right.
Well, I wasn't here!

46:48.473 --> 46:50.849
[ Groaning ]

46:52.977 --> 46:54.978
dd [ Instrumental Interlude ]

47:02.987 --> 47:05.447
He's as nervous as a bride.

47:05.573 --> 47:07.824
One might think
they were going to hang him.

47:10.161 --> 47:12.662
It's up to you.
Now, tell them.

47:12.788 --> 47:14.498
What have I got
to do with it?

47:14.624 --> 47:18.502
You're handling the...
details of the wedding.

47:18.628 --> 47:20.962
